1
00:00:21,070 --> 00:00:24,180
♪The breeze of the 1990s drifts by♪

2
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:27,180
♪Memories slowly flicker past♪

3
00:00:27,650 --> 00:00:31,430
♪My heartbeat
rises and falls with the tune♪

4
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:34,580
♪The story quietly begins here♪

5
00:00:35,330 --> 00:00:38,640
♪Under the dim lights, our eyes meet♪

6
00:00:38,710 --> 00:00:41,850
♪Time seems to stand still♪

7
00:00:42,350 --> 00:00:45,990
♪Your smile
breaks through the clouds like sun♪

8
00:00:46,060 --> 00:00:49,150
♪Melting the snow deep in my heart♪

9
00:00:49,580 --> 00:00:53,090
♪Street posters spread signals of love♪

10
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:56,110
♪Our story slowly begins to ferment♪

11
00:00:56,800 --> 00:01:00,730
♪Hand in hand,
going through every dusk corner♪

12
00:01:00,930 --> 00:01:04,800
♪The taste of happiness is so subtle♪

13
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:08,740
♪Crossing back to the 1990s stage♪

14
00:01:09,150 --> 00:01:12,480
♪You're my most beautiful surprise♪

15
00:01:12,790 --> 00:01:16,210
♪Love's flame burns within my heart♪

16
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:19,710
♪Not afraid of obstacles ahead♪

17
00:01:20,180 --> 00:01:23,560
♪Sway with the rhythm.
Feel your heart pound♪

18
00:01:23,660 --> 00:01:27,150
♪This love will never change♪

19
00:01:27,950 --> 00:01:35,080
♪We hold tight in this crazy era♪

20
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:40,060
♪1990s love is what we rely on♪

21
00:01:40,100 --> 00:01:42,070
=Once More Love in 1995=

22
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:45,000
=Episode 14=

23
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,359
Why are you here?

24
00:02:09,679 --> 00:02:11,760
Helping Qin Jiamin gather information?

25
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:13,959
I'm also Shanshan's brother.

26
00:02:14,239 --> 00:02:15,679
I just worry about her progress.

27
00:02:16,239 --> 00:02:17,359
You can relax.

28
00:02:17,760 --> 00:02:20,079
Shanshan is doing very well.

29
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:24,987
Do you really think this method

30
00:02:25,320 --> 00:02:26,760
is better than letting Shanshan

31
00:02:27,050 --> 00:02:28,010
study abroad?

32
00:02:28,959 --> 00:02:29,760
What do you mean?

33
00:02:30,559 --> 00:02:31,880
Being Publicity Department's manager

34
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:33,359
and spokesperson

35
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:34,839
was your idea.

36
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:36,519
You like competition,

37
00:02:36,639 --> 00:02:37,959
but Shanshan doesn't.

38
00:02:38,639 --> 00:02:40,239
I just think Shanshan's

39
00:02:41,359 --> 00:02:42,559
been smiling less lately.

40
00:02:43,359 --> 00:02:44,720
I think she's not happy.

41
00:02:44,959 --> 00:02:46,079
This isn't her dream.

42
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:48,559
You want to talk to me
about happy education?

43
00:02:49,239 --> 00:02:52,440
Shanshan finally
has interest and drive for Jinxin.

44
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:54,359
You encourage her to chase dreams.

45
00:02:55,679 --> 00:02:58,119
Are you afraid
she'll take your power in Jinxin

46
00:02:58,119 --> 00:03:00,175
if she becomes famous?

47
00:03:00,359 --> 00:03:02,880
Do you care so much
about her control in Jinxin?

48
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:05,300
Are you doing it for her

49
00:03:05,839 --> 00:03:07,480
or fulfilling your obsession?

50
00:03:12,359 --> 00:03:13,160
Zhuang Yan.

51
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:15,119
You're all thorns,

52
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:16,480
but Shanshan isn't.

53
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:18,639
I don't want her to grow sharp edges.

54
00:03:19,639 --> 00:03:20,440
Yeah.

55
00:03:21,559 --> 00:03:22,959
I'm all thorns

56
00:03:23,679 --> 00:03:25,079
because of all of you.

57
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:39,480
Ah.

58
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:41,920
Oh.

59
00:03:42,559 --> 00:03:44,160
Today was exhausting.

60
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:45,359
Yeah, really exhausting.

61
00:03:49,119 --> 00:03:50,239
Have you noticed?

62
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:52,399
How many of your ads
were on the street today?

63
00:03:54,559 --> 00:03:55,559
Eight.

64
00:03:56,359 --> 00:03:59,760
One of them is this big.

65
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:04,150
Zhuang Shanshan, you're famous now.

66
00:04:04,519 --> 00:04:06,920
You're Jinxin's walking billboard
from now on.

67
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,440
Forget about general manager.

68
00:04:09,559 --> 00:04:12,359
Even being a chairman is within reach.

69
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:14,320
Happy?

70
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:15,079
I surrender.

71
00:04:15,079 --> 00:04:16,439
Hahaha, happy?

72
00:04:16,439 --> 00:04:19,640
Yan, you overestimate me.

73
00:04:20,439 --> 00:04:22,239
There are so many seniors
in the company.

74
00:04:22,280 --> 00:04:23,520
I've only joined a few days.

75
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:24,559
I'm not qualified.

76
00:04:26,679 --> 00:04:27,559
Besides,

77
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:30,759
I plan to leave
after finishing my tasks.

78
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:32,520
What?

79
00:04:33,080 --> 00:04:34,640
During these days at Jinxin,

80
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:37,160
Qin and you
taught me a lot of things.

81
00:04:37,319 --> 00:04:39,480
I used to avoid setbacks,

82
00:04:39,559 --> 00:04:42,480
but now I have the courage to face them.

83
00:04:44,119 --> 00:04:44,920
Yan.

84
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:47,160
I've contacted Juilliard School.

85
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:49,759
I want to return to the stage.

86
00:04:51,840 --> 00:04:54,080
But you just found
your footing at Jinxin.

87
00:04:54,239 --> 00:04:55,337
Leaving now

88
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:58,337
would waste all my efforts and planning.

89
00:04:59,040 --> 00:04:59,840
Yan.

90
00:05:00,319 --> 00:05:02,359
you came to Jinxin for me, right?

91
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:05,359
You wanted to help me stand firm.

92
00:05:06,359 --> 00:05:08,239
I know you trust Qin Mo now,

93
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,679
but the future is unknown.

94
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:11,679
It's better

95
00:05:11,679 --> 00:05:13,040
to hold on to your own things.

96
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:15,280
At least take a spot,

97
00:05:15,679 --> 00:05:16,720
just in case.

98
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:19,520
Yan, you've been here long.

99
00:05:19,759 --> 00:05:22,439
How do you think
Qin has managed Jinxin?

100
00:05:23,359 --> 00:05:26,319
He does manage it well.

101
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,280
I admit

102
00:05:30,359 --> 00:05:32,687
he's an excellent
businessman and manager.

103
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:35,319
But returning things
to the rightful owner is only fair.

104
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:37,480
After you take back Jinxin,

105
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:39,080
you can still hire Qin Mo to help.

106
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:42,160
Then if I say

107
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,559
Jinxin is also mine now?

108
00:05:44,319 --> 00:05:44,840
Huh?

109
00:05:46,160 --> 00:05:47,359
You heard right.

110
00:05:47,359 --> 00:05:48,640
Jinxin is mine.

111
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:52,759
Then what about Qin Mo?

112
00:05:53,359 --> 00:05:54,280
Nominal head of the company?

113
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:57,439
Three years ago,
my dad's strategy mistake

114
00:05:57,439 --> 00:05:58,840
almost bankrupt Jinxin.

115
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:01,199
Boss.

116
00:06:01,439 --> 00:06:02,960
You asked me to check Zhuang Yan,

117
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:04,112
and now there's news.

118
00:06:12,025 --> 00:06:14,412
(Zhuang Yan)

119
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:19,960
So,

120
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:24,879
Qin Mo manages Jinxin on the surface,

121
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,879
but he's actually
protecting your family's business?

122
00:06:29,119 --> 00:06:29,840
Yes.

123
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:31,920
Qin has been helping me
withstand the pressure,

124
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:33,920
so I can focus on my own stuff.

125
00:06:34,759 --> 00:06:36,920
Is this really the Qin Mo I know?

126
00:06:38,119 --> 00:06:39,720
Isn't he like an angel?

127
00:06:40,280 --> 00:06:41,439
Yan.

128
00:06:41,439 --> 00:06:43,319
You probably don't know Qin well.

129
00:06:43,319 --> 00:06:45,187
He really is a good person.

130
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:47,679
He wants no profit, no gain.

131
00:06:47,759 --> 00:06:48,480
Grateful and loyal.

132
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:49,559
He keeps his promise.

133
00:06:49,679 --> 00:06:51,160
Jiamin is his sister.

134
00:06:51,319 --> 00:06:53,080
He knows she dislikes me.

135
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:55,559
For years he kept her in Yuecheng

136
00:06:55,837 --> 00:06:57,319
and never mentioned ownership of Jinxin

137
00:06:57,319 --> 00:06:58,759
to anyone else.

138
00:06:58,759 --> 00:06:59,720
All to protect me.

139
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:02,759
Why does he never explain?

140
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:03,999
He lets me misunderstand.

141
00:07:04,840 --> 00:07:06,559
You should ask Qin that.

142
00:07:08,759 --> 00:07:09,550
Yan.

143
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:11,160
You've been like a female warrior,

144
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,640
charging nonstop forward.

145
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:14,720
It's time to look back.

146
00:07:14,759 --> 00:07:17,520
Someone has silently been guarding you.

147
00:07:33,759 --> 00:07:34,679
You're back.

148
00:07:37,359 --> 00:07:38,840
What is this?

149
00:07:40,439 --> 00:07:42,520
I want to treat you to a meal.

150
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:45,400
I wonder if you'll accept.

151
00:07:47,119 --> 00:07:48,759
Why are you suddenly so nice to me?

152
00:07:49,879 --> 00:07:51,319
If there's something, just ask me.

153
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,720
I'm not used to you doing this.

154
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,640
Not used to me treating you well?

155
00:07:57,119 --> 00:07:57,960
You like to suffer?

156
00:07:59,319 --> 00:08:01,119
Don't worry. It's safe.

157
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:02,759
I just bought it from outside.

158
00:08:07,575 --> 00:08:09,525
(Folder)

159
00:08:15,550 --> 00:08:16,351
Qin Mo.

160
00:08:18,225 --> 00:08:19,186
A toast to you.

161
00:08:19,975 --> 00:08:21,614
It's to thank you

162
00:08:22,100 --> 00:08:23,080
and to apologize to you.

163
00:08:23,559 --> 00:08:25,040
Shanshan told me

164
00:08:25,559 --> 00:08:27,312
what happened between you two.

165
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:30,439
I sincerely thank you

166
00:08:30,439 --> 00:08:33,520
for treating Shanshan well
while I was gone.

167
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:36,280
I want her happy,

168
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:39,479
but I never asked her

169
00:08:39,479 --> 00:08:40,959
what she really wanted.

170
00:08:42,040 --> 00:08:44,520
You let her live the life she wants.

171
00:08:46,679 --> 00:08:50,319
I also apologize
for my prejudice toward you.

172
00:08:50,719 --> 00:08:53,040
I always thought
you took Jinxin from Shanshan.

173
00:08:54,479 --> 00:08:55,559
I'm always going against you

174
00:08:55,559 --> 00:08:56,920
and even wanted to kick you out.

175
00:08:59,439 --> 00:09:00,240
I'm sorry.

176
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:07,439
It was all for Shanshan.

177
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:08,679
It's okay.

178
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:10,559
So you forgive me?

179
00:09:11,479 --> 00:09:12,839
If you forgive me,

180
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:13,920
then drink it all.

181
00:09:22,319 --> 00:09:23,160
Awesome.

182
00:09:25,439 --> 00:09:26,079
Alright.

183
00:09:26,799 --> 00:09:27,880
Next,

184
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:29,920
I'll start asking questions.

185
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:33,319
Since I joined Jinxin,

186
00:09:33,319 --> 00:09:34,640
I had misunderstandings about you.

187
00:09:34,640 --> 00:09:36,319
Why never explain yourself?

188
00:09:37,479 --> 00:09:38,479
I was curious.

189
00:09:39,559 --> 00:09:40,250
Curious?

190
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,719
Since we met,

191
00:09:46,880 --> 00:09:48,719
you were like a trouble
that's everywhere.

192
00:09:49,559 --> 00:09:51,240
From coming home with me

193
00:09:51,319 --> 00:09:53,760
to doing everything to join Jinxin,

194
00:09:54,760 --> 00:09:56,559
I couldn't tell your intentions,

195
00:09:56,559 --> 00:09:57,760
so I couldn't explain.

196
00:09:58,559 --> 00:09:59,599
Later I realized

197
00:10:00,479 --> 00:10:02,439
you did all this for Shanshan,

198
00:10:03,079 --> 00:10:04,880
so I saw no need to explain.

199
00:10:05,439 --> 00:10:06,760
Because at least

200
00:10:07,079 --> 00:10:08,240
our goals align.

201
00:10:09,479 --> 00:10:10,280
Oh.

202
00:10:10,640 --> 00:10:12,040
Let me be honest.

203
00:10:12,479 --> 00:10:13,839
I joined Jinxin

204
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:15,319
to compete with you for the company.

205
00:10:16,079 --> 00:10:17,360
I've been looking for chances.

206
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,360
It gave me a headache.

207
00:10:19,959 --> 00:10:22,337
I even thought about marrying you,

208
00:10:22,520 --> 00:10:24,760
turning Jinxin into marital property.

209
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:27,559
I could split it after divorce

210
00:10:27,559 --> 00:10:29,599
and leave half for Shanshan.

211
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:34,559
I don't get

212
00:10:34,559 --> 00:10:35,959
why you think

213
00:10:36,040 --> 00:10:37,612
marrying me must mean divorce.

214
00:10:41,040 --> 00:10:42,640
You really catch the key points.

215
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:58,559
Now that we've cleared things up,

216
00:10:58,920 --> 00:11:00,160
I have one last question.

217
00:11:00,760 --> 00:11:02,360
I hope you'll answer honestly.

218
00:11:03,760 --> 00:11:04,520
Go ahead.

219
00:11:07,319 --> 00:11:08,959
Are you really Zhuang Yan?

220
00:11:14,839 --> 00:11:15,640
Yes.

221
00:11:28,862 --> 00:11:32,700
(Folder, Zhuang Yan)

222
00:11:40,280 --> 00:11:43,880
- Shanshan.
- Zhuang Shanshan.

223
00:11:45,760 --> 00:11:46,479
Ah.

224
00:11:46,479 --> 00:11:47,760
Everyone, stay in order.

225
00:11:47,760 --> 00:11:48,679
Queue properly.

226
00:11:49,079 --> 00:11:51,319
(Haicheng International Food Fair)
Get your meet-and-greet numbers here.

227
00:11:51,920 --> 00:11:53,360
- Okay.
- Okay.

228
00:11:58,160 --> 00:11:59,599
118.

229
00:12:00,079 --> 00:12:01,120
119.

230
00:12:04,040 --> 00:12:05,479
Li, how's your side?

231
00:12:05,479 --> 00:12:06,479
173 orders.

232
00:12:06,679 --> 00:12:08,040
With mine, that's 400.

233
00:12:08,500 --> 00:12:09,699
Victory is ours.

234
00:12:12,875 --> 00:12:13,799
Let me see.

235
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:16,400
Who's promoting themselves here?

236
00:12:17,079 --> 00:12:17,920
You?

237
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,559
Can I use my own vinegar?

238
00:12:19,559 --> 00:12:20,640
I'll dip it with dumplings.

239
00:12:20,640 --> 00:12:21,360
Security.

240
00:12:21,760 --> 00:12:23,559
Someone's causing trouble.

241
00:12:23,880 --> 00:12:24,920
No.

242
00:12:24,920 --> 00:12:27,360
We're here to attend the fair.

243
00:12:27,920 --> 00:12:30,520
Ms. Zhuang, I just have one question.

244
00:12:30,850 --> 00:12:32,529
Guolong Food

245
00:12:32,637 --> 00:12:35,160
uses real ingredients to compete.
What about you?

246
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:36,000
You?

247
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:38,559
Put a few girls on stage and do this.

248
00:12:38,559 --> 00:12:40,160
Aren't you ashamed?

249
00:12:40,319 --> 00:12:40,725
Huh?

250
00:12:41,160 --> 00:12:43,079
I want to ask

251
00:12:43,199 --> 00:12:44,625
if Jinxin is a proper company?

252
00:12:44,839 --> 00:12:47,240
You call those few ingredients real?

253
00:12:48,559 --> 00:12:51,250
I guess you're just jealous.

254
00:12:52,559 --> 00:12:54,525
How many orders has Guolong Food signed?

255
00:12:54,530 --> 00:12:56,240
I hope it won't be left expired
due to lack of business.

256
00:12:58,719 --> 00:13:00,959
You're still sharp-tongued.

257
00:13:01,160 --> 00:13:02,319
Likewise.

258
00:13:02,319 --> 00:13:03,880
You're still disgusting.

259
00:13:04,280 --> 00:13:05,719
Who are you calling disgusting?

260
00:13:06,160 --> 00:13:06,599
Hey.

261
00:13:09,679 --> 00:13:10,400
Hey.

262
00:13:10,475 --> 00:13:12,435
You just attacked me.

263
00:13:12,559 --> 00:13:13,475
Didn't you start it first?

264
00:13:14,280 --> 00:13:14,959
Zhang Guolong.

265
00:13:15,400 --> 00:13:16,640
If you're interested in our products,

266
00:13:17,640 --> 00:13:19,187
queue properly in the back.

267
00:13:20,040 --> 00:13:20,599
Bah.

268
00:13:21,079 --> 00:13:22,487
I don't even want your trash.

269
00:13:22,679 --> 00:13:23,559
What did you say?

270
00:13:24,520 --> 00:13:26,479
I won't stoop to your level.

271
00:13:34,479 --> 00:13:34,839
Li.

272
00:13:35,599 --> 00:13:36,439
Clear them out.

273
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:38,199
Clear?

274
00:13:38,479 --> 00:13:39,040
Mo.

275
00:13:39,040 --> 00:13:40,120
Do you think I'm trash?

276
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:41,559
Can't I approach Jinxin?

277
00:13:41,559 --> 00:13:44,439
The moment you side with Zhang Guolong,

278
00:13:44,839 --> 00:13:46,319
you lose that right.

279
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:48,439
You chose your path.

280
00:13:48,640 --> 00:13:49,559
Don't blame others.

281
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:50,880
Jiamin.

282
00:13:50,880 --> 00:13:52,280
As long as you keep Jinxin's shares,

283
00:13:52,280 --> 00:13:53,525
it's not too late.

284
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:56,520
Zhuang Shanshan, don't be too smug.

285
00:13:56,559 --> 00:13:57,760
It's not over yet.

286
00:13:57,760 --> 00:13:58,719
We don't know the result.

287
00:13:59,040 --> 00:14:00,719
Is this how you do business?

288
00:14:01,400 --> 00:14:02,280
What happened?

289
00:14:02,280 --> 00:14:03,862
You sent us expired food.

290
00:14:03,920 --> 00:14:04,520
Huh?

291
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:07,120
How could you be so unscrupulous?

292
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:09,520
- Refund!
- Refund!

293
00:14:09,760 --> 00:14:11,640
- Refund!
- Refund!

294
00:14:11,959 --> 00:14:13,559
- Refund!
- Refund!

295
00:14:13,719 --> 00:14:15,199
- Refund!
- Refund!

296
00:14:15,479 --> 00:14:16,959
- Refund!
- Refund!

297
00:14:16,959 --> 00:14:18,079
Hurry, refund.

298
00:14:36,150 --> 00:14:39,788
♪The old dial tone circles in my ear♪

299
00:14:39,913 --> 00:14:43,225
♪Faded tickets point to a cicada summer♪

300
00:14:43,388 --> 00:14:46,975
♪The videotape
whispers your image in the frame♪

301
00:14:47,275 --> 00:14:50,563
♪Against the light, the plaid shirt
reveals a clear and transparent smile♪

302
00:14:50,788 --> 00:14:54,413
♪I'm a clumsy guest in a frozen scene♪

303
00:14:54,575 --> 00:14:57,913
♪How do I answer familiar lines?♪

304
00:14:57,988 --> 00:15:01,700
♪I know
the train will leave this station♪

305
00:15:01,750 --> 00:15:05,613
♪I know the ending's in a faded future♪

306
00:15:05,675 --> 00:15:11,725
♪Yet I want to approach that warmth♪

307
00:15:12,900 --> 00:15:19,638
♪Even one second rewrites missed lines♪

308
00:15:19,925 --> 00:15:24,200
♪Rewind to 1995,
back to the street we met♪

309
00:15:24,200 --> 00:15:27,500
♪Wind blows through the sycamore leaves
and lands on your shoulder♪

310
00:15:27,575 --> 00:15:31,875
♪I wish I could pause and stop time♪

311
00:15:31,938 --> 00:15:35,588
♪Let unspoken love
be preserved forever as amber♪

312
00:15:35,588 --> 00:15:39,150
♪Rewind to 1995,
gentle touch of fingertips♪

313
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:42,463
♪Star sparks in your eyes burn my chest♪

314
00:15:42,463 --> 00:15:46,213
♪This looping script
is beyond my saving♪

315
00:15:46,213 --> 00:15:52,925
♪I can only stay with you till the end
in this inverted hourglass♪
